title: Sesame Beef Bites
ingredients: ['2 tablespoons sesame oil', '1 tablespoon rice vinegar', '1 spring onion, minced', '1 clove garlic, minced', '2 teaspoons hoisin sauce', '1/4 teaspoon chilli garlic sauce', '450g beef fillet, cut into 2cm cubes', '4 tablespoons teriyaki sauce', '1/2 teaspoon sesame seeds']
